ZH: 我过去常常和朋友一起去踢足球。
EN: In the past, I used to play soccer with friends often.

ZH: 他过去有一个很有趣的工作。
EN: He used to have a very interesting job in the past.

ZH: 过去的每一天我都会去健身房锻炼。
EN: Every day in the past, I used to go to the gym to work out.

ZH: 我小时候过去常常爬树。
EN: When I was a child, I used to climb trees often.

ZH: 去年过去全家人去旅行了。
EN: Last year, the whole family went on a trip together.

ZH: 过去我们家住在农村。
EN: In the past, our family used to live in the countryside.

ZH: 我在大学时代过去会参加各种社团活动。
EN: During my time in college, I used to participate in various clubs.

ZH: 她过去是一个非常有名的歌手。
EN: She used to be a very famous singer in the past.

ZH: 我过去总是迟到。
EN: I used to always be late in the past.

ZH: 过去的生活比现在简单多了。
EN: Life in the past was much simpler than it is now.

ZH: 她小时候经常过去看电影。
EN: When she was a child, she used to watch movies often.

ZH: 我过去不喜欢吃辣的东西。
EN: I used to not like spicy food in the past.

ZH: 过去的时光总是过得很快。
EN: Time always passed quickly in the past.

ZH: 我过去觉得学习很烦人。
EN: I used to find studying annoying in the past.

ZH: 我们过去经常出去玩。
EN: We used to go out to play often in the past.

ZH: 过去的一切都已经变了。
EN: Everything in the past has already changed.

ZH: 我过去从来没有去过海边。
EN: I have never been to the seaside in the past.

ZH: 那件事情在过去就算结束了。
EN: That matter has already ended in the past.

ZH: 过去我不知道她的电话号码。
EN: I didn't know her phone number in the past.

ZH: 你过去常常看漫画吗？
EN: Did you used to read comics often in the past?
